  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Iron_Islands.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bd/Iron_Islands.jpg/350px-Iron_Islands.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/bd/Iron_Islands.jpg/525px-Iron_Islands.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/bd/Iron_Islands.jpg/700px-Iron_Islands.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Iron_Islands.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Sealskin Point is located at the northern coast of <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a>, northwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafmap_of_the_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafmap_of_the_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Sealskin Point</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd_of_Sealskin_Point\" title=\"House Farwynd of Sealskin Point\">House Farwynd of Sealskin Point</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sealskin_Point&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite